{"word":"Πυανόψια","slug":"Πυανόψια","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n91305\" key=\"*puano/yia\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">Πῠᾰνόψια</orth> (sc. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἱερά</foreign>), <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">τά</gen>, an Athenian festival in the month <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">Πυανοψιών</foreign>, in honour of Apollo, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0034.tlg002:84\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Lycurg.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Fr.\">Fr.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">84</biblScope> </bibl>: elsewh. written <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">Πυανέψια</orth> (cf. sq.) and expld. fr. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">πύανον ἕψειν</foreign>, of a dish of beans cooked and offered, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0007.tlg001:22\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Plu.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Thes.\">Thes.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">22</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0008.tlg001.perseus-grc1:10:408a\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ath.\">Ath.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">10.408a</biblScope></bibl>, etc.; acc. to Lycurg.l.c. the other Greeks called it <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">Πανόψια </orth>( <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">Πανοψίαν</orth> codd.).</entryFree>"}]}